com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Class OperatingSystemType

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.emf.common.util.AbstractEnumerator
      com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os.OperatingSystemType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, org.eclipse.emf.common.util.Enumerator
public final class OperatingSystemType
extends org.eclipse.emf.common.util.AbstractEnumerator

A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Operating System Type', and utility methods for working with them. This type defines operating system types known to be allowed by TPM Because list is not exclusive, these values are only used during validation.

See Also:
OsPackage.getOperatingSystemType(), Serialized Form
